main event: On 18 July 1949, two round objects were observed flying in an easterly direction at a high rate of speed over Fairfield Suisun AFB, California.
interesting points: The objects were described as being dull white or silver in color., Witnesses included S/Sgt, Cpl, and Pvt from the USAF., The objects were reported to be traveling faster than a C-82 aircraft which was overhead., The sighting lasted only 4-5 seconds with no sound or visible trail., There were no photographs available in the report.
sighted object: two round objects in the sky
witness description: S/Sgt, Cpl, Pvt, all from the USAF
